1
00:00:02,306 --> 00:00:04,488
It isn't often that you see Mr. Roosevelt relaxing.

2
00:00:04,929 --> 00:00:10,292
Like Mr. Churchill, this other great man has little time or inclination to take it easy while so much remains to be done.

3
00:00:10,933 --> 00:00:15,557
But it's good to see that the president has a little private life, or did have until the cameraman came in.

4
00:00:15,577 --> 00:00:21,501
The little girl is Diana, daughter of Mr. Harry Hopkins, and the dog is Mr. Roosevelt's good companion Fala.

5
00:00:22,361 --> 00:00:23,242
What's in the scrapbook?

6
00:00:23,823 --> 00:00:25,885
Pictures that in their day were front page news.

7
00:00:26,425 --> 00:00:28,306
Fala was in on that important occasion also.

8
00:00:31,402 --> 00:00:37,292
In the middle of this most terrible war it's pleasant to recall that presidents and ministers and royalty are just... It helps you to keep sane.

9
00:00:37,353 --> 00:00:41,341
After the war there'll be more room in the daily round for present hours spent like this.
